  "title": "Public Relations Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible in managing and enhancing the company's image and reputation in the market through executing an array of marketing communication strategies</li>\n  <li>Organize and execute events that promotes the company's business and reputation within the construction industry, as well as key target markets</li>\n  <li>Manage media relations</li>\n  <li>Engage and inform stakeholders of the company's activities through a variety of marketing communications strategies, including newsletter, circulars, marketing campaigns etc</li>\n  <li>Engage with customers regularly and manage their complaints and suggestions, working with the management team to formulate the best possible solutions to address customer concerns</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a Diploma or Degree in Communications / Marketing</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of work experience in Public Relations, preferably with experience as a PRO in the Construction industry for LTA projects</li>\n  <li>Have excellent communication skills (oral and written).</li>\n  <li>Excellent client management skills, able to engage effectively with customers and stake holders</li>\n  <li>Time management skills, ability to handle multiple priorities and engage with different levels of the organization</li>\n</ul>",
